{"data":[{"date":"08:40 23/06","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC: \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 vua","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/23/du-am-hagl-32-sai-gon-fc-dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng lu\u00f4n thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u00ec l\u1ee3m v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 thua HAGL nh\u01b0 c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 u\u1ec3 o\u1ea3i trong t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 l\u1ecfng l\u1ebbo trong ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.</h2><h2>S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1eebng &lsquo;h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t&rsquo; H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i&hellip;</h2>\r\n<h2><o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi\u1ebfn CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00fa \u00fd c\u1ee7a d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n b\u1edfi vi\u1ec7c c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f3 ch\u1ee9 ch\u01b0a n\u00f3i t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 c\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eadm. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ebf m\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u1eabn l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh \u1edf ngay l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 vua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC \u0110\u00e2u r\u1ed3i k\u1ebb h\u1ea1 s\u00e1t nh\u00e0 vua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/Du-am-HAGL-3-2-Sai-Gon-FC-Dau-roi-ke-ha-sat-nha-vua-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>S\u00e0i G\u00f2n b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a l\u00e2u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f4 di\u1ec5n s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh qu\u1eadt c\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1eb1ng 11 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfm ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch t\u1edbi 10 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 b\u00e1m \u0111u\u1ed5i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC v\u00e0 t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1, h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ee9ng minh s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh khi &lsquo;h\u1ea1 \u0111\u1eb9p&rsquo; th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Chu \u0110\u00ecnh Nghi\u00eam trong c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n b\u1ecb nghi ng\u1edd b\u1edfi t\u00ednh minh b\u1ea1ch, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 khi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t hay d\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh qua nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>&hellip; nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc HAGL<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u0111\u00f3, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Pleiku c\u1ee7a HAGL v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u 22/6. N\u1ebfu th\u1eafng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em s\u1ebd &lsquo;an to\u00e0n&rsquo; nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu thua, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u00f3ng gi\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">G\u1eb7p HAGL, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC r\u1ea5t khao kh\u00e1t c\u00f3 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 x\u1ea3y ra. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t HAGL s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn ra v\u1ec1 tay tr\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HAGL\" title=\"HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/23/SG-GL6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><i>D\u01b0 \u00e2m HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch</i></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">90 ph\u00fat t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai, d\u00f9 c\u00f3 s\u1edbm c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng s\u00fat ph\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m \u1edf kh\u00e2u ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n thua t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao HAGL. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 nh\u1eadn ra CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y v\u1eabn l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e8 b\u1eb9p H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra v\u00f4 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai v\u1ed1n v\u1eeba tr\u1ea3i qua chu\u1ed7i 3 tr\u1eadn thua li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i V-League 2018.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1eadn hay, tr\u1eadn d\u1edf, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn HLV T\u00e0i Em s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ec7n minh cho th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 c\u0169ng s\u1ebd ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f2n tinh th\u1ea7n Iceland n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap HLV T\u00e0i Em c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y \u00edt h\u00f4m, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n t\u1eebng cho bi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 tham kh\u1ea3o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Iceland tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u00f3 v\u1edbi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Nh\u01b0ng tr\u1edb tr\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n sinh n\u0103m 1982 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Ch\u1eb7ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00f2n r\u1ea5t d\u00e0i<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Thua ng\u01b0\u1ee3c HAGL, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u1ea7n qu\u00ean chi\u1ebfn t\u00edch phi th\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u1edf v\u00f2ng 14 v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edbm tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ea5t v\u00e0 d\u1ed3n s\u1ee9c cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. Khi m\u00e0 kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh s\u1ebd tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng sau 12 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 T\u00e0i Em s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Vinh g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111ang c\u1ea1nh tranh tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp su\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng l\u00e0 SLNA. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u 6 \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i G\u00f2n s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01a1 c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i, n\u1ebfu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec5n c\u1ea3nh ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng ch\u01a1i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng Nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a t\u1edbi c\u0169ng \u0111ang hi\u1ec7n ra r\u00f5 n\u00e9t h\u01a1n v\u1edbi h\u1ecd.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/BXH-sau-vong-15-V-League.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>BXH V-League 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3774","checkdouble":"189318"},{"date":"20:22 22/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i xem nh\u1eb9 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/nguoi-thai-xem-nhe-u19-viet-nam-truoc-them-giai-u19-dong-nam-a.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u khu v\u1ef1c s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan, Narakorn Noomchansakul \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam.</h2><h2>Sao U19 Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1eeb ng\u00e0y 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 14/7 t\u1ea1i Jakarta (Indonesia). \u1ede gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay, l\u00e1 phi\u1ebfu b\u1ed1c th\u0103m \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam\u00a0v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng A c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ea1nh l\u00e0 ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Indonesia, Th\u00e1i Lan, Singapore, L\u00e0o, Philippines. B\u1ea3ng B c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a Malaysia, Myanmar, \u0110\u00f4ng Timor, Campuchia v\u00e0 Brunei.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i xem nh\u1eb9 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i xem nh\u1eb9 U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/U19-Thai-Lan-danh-gia-thap-U19-Viet-Nam-truoc-them-giai-U19-DNA-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Narakorn Noomchansakul\u00a0kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t gi\u1ea3i. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn 3 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra hai t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 U19 Th\u00e1i Lan Narakorn Noomchansakul th\u00ec U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i lo ng\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0\"T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 U19 Indonesia v\u00e0 U19 Malaysia s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t d\u00e0n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb t\u00e0i n\u0103ng, \u00edt s\u1ef1 bi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9ng. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 r\u1ea5t v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua h\u1ecd. U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 m\u1ea1nh\u201d, Noomchansakul t\u00e2m s\u1ef1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u0169ng ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u khi m\u00e0 ngay c\u1ea3 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn nh\u01b0 l\u1ee9a c\u1ee7a Quang H\u1ea3i hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c. Sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng t\u01b0ng b\u1eebng tr\u01b0\u1edbc CLB Meizhou Meixian Techand, \u0111\u1ebfn ng\u00e0y 24/6 t\u1edbi, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi qu\u00e2n xanh n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd h\u01a1n, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i B c\u1ee7a CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 \u2018thu\u1ed1c th\u1eed m\u1ea1nh\u2019 v\u1edbi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n nh\u1eb1m chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 2018 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3773","checkdouble":"189289"},{"date":"20:56 22/06","title":"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng nh\u1ecdc c\u1ee7a HAGL tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/thay-gi-sau-tran-thang-nhoc-cua-hagl-truoc-sai-gon-fc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong l\u1ea7n t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Pleiku chi\u1ec1u 22/6, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f2i n\u1ee3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sau tr\u1eadn thua \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-2. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y.</h2><h2>1. Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1edbi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat c\u00f3 phong \u0111\u1ed9 ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t cho HAGL \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00e2n chuy\u1ec1n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i B\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ghi nh\u1eefng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft cho HAGL tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y, d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c t\u1ea1o si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m t\u1eeb c\u00e1i ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i \u2018r\u1ea5t d\u1ebbo\u2019 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eabn khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi khi ghi b\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u. D\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao 1m65 nh\u01b0ng trong t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a HAGL, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1eadt cao \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Da-Nang-2-1-HAGL-Chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. \u1ea2nh: Zing.vn</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang \u1edf trong nh\u1eefng ng\u00e0y th\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9, m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tham d\u1ef1 ASIAD 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau xa v\u1eddi v\u1edbi ch\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 \u0111i\u1ec3n trai n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>2. HAGL c\u1ea7n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n trong c\u00e1c pha chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t S\u00e0i G\u00f2n co c\u1ee5m ph\u00f2ng c\u1ef1, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL kh\u00f4ng kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn. H\u1ecd c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 tung ra nh\u1eefng pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc n\u00e9t h\u01a1n. Tuy nhi\u00ean t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u201cG\u1ed7\u201d l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5p khi b\u00f3ng ch\u1ec9 lu\u1ea9n qu\u1ea9n ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i b\u1ecb ph\u00e1.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u1ea3 C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, Xu\u00e2n Tr\u01b0\u1eddng hay c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 HAGL \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n trong vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi ch\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. \u1ede nhi\u1ec1u pha t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nguy hi\u1ec3m, c\u00e1c pha chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i thi\u1ebfu l\u1ef1c ho\u1eb7c thi\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1edbi \u0111\u00fang v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, d\u1eabn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb7t c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf kh\u00f3 khi nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng. N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 trau chu\u1ed1t h\u01a1n trong c\u00e1c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u201cG\u1ed7\u201d \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u00e0 h\u01a1n th\u1ebf. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>3. Da Sylva ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c n\u1ed5 s\u00fang<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, Da Sylva ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cho S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC, v\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, ngo\u1ea1i binh n\u00e0y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y c\u00e1i duy\u00ean ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai sau pha \u0111i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea5u \u0111i s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt l\u00e0 Da Sylva \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 CLB HAGL s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nguy\u00ean h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 n\u1ed9i, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 Da Sylva, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba ghi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa poker b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Da Sylva (phai) tiep tuc ghi ban vao luoi HAGL\" title=\"Da Sylva (ph\u1ea3i) ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/05_saigon_hagl_140418_anhkhahoa06_tydi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Da Sylva (ph\u1ea3i) ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi HAGL</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n S\u00e0i G\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. V\u1edbi th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, Da Sylva \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi s\u1ef1 truy c\u1ea3n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 HAGL \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn. Nh\u01b0ng \u1edf nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, ngo\u1ea1i binh c\u1ee7a S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u1ea1i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 k\u00e9m duy\u00ean c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111i ch\u1ec7ch c\u1ed9t d\u1ecdc khung th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u1ea3i t\u1edbi t\u1edbi cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Da Sylva m\u1edbi d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng \u0111i l\u1ecdt qua h\u00e1ng th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi. C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Da Sylva kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m m\u00e0 l\u1ed7i thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n HAGL.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u1eabu sao v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u1eeba qua, ngo\u1ea1i binh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 9 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu gi\u1eef v\u1eefng phong \u0111\u1ed9 anh ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp Oseni c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i trong danh s\u00e1ch Vua ph\u00e1 l\u01b0\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<h2>4. Ngo\u1ea1i binh m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a G\u1ed7 ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ec3\u00a0l\u1ea1i d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, CLB HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi mang t\u00ean Osmar Moreira, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i \u0111\u00e3 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o SLNA. H\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a, ng\u00f4i sao Brazil t\u1eebng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Ngh\u1ec7 khi ghi\u00a01 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p 1 pha ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u SLNA - Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (2 - 2).<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Khi m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra su\u00f4n s\u1ebb, Osmar b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1ecb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 h\u01a1n 2 th\u00e1ng. Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng Osmar \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 b\u1ecb SLNA th\u1ea3i lo\u1ea1i sau khi l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i k\u1ebft th\u00fac.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ph\u1ed1 n\u00fai n\u01a1i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2016, Osmar \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 \u0103n \u00fd v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i trong c\u00e1c pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 anh c\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00ec v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ngon \u0103n nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 ngo\u1ea1i binh n\u00e0y c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng anh \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n S\u00e0i G\u00f2n song qu\u1ea3 t\u1ea1t b\u00ean c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a V\u0103n Thanh \u1edf ph\u00fat 60, tuy nhi\u00ean khi c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n Osmar l\u1ea1i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111i v\u1ecdt x\u00e0 trong s\u1ef1 nu\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfc c\u1ee7a NHM \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai.</p>\r\n<h2>5. V\u1ecb tr\u00ed hai \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean BXH<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 20 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean gi\u1eef h\u1ea1ng 7 tr\u00ean BXH. Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a HAGL v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec l\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 5 \u0111i\u1ec3m khi th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan Thanh H\u00f9ng c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u2018ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a\u2019 \u1edf v\u00f2ng n\u00e0y ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Kh\u00e1nh H\u00f2a. N\u1ebfu thi \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi, HAGL c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1ed1p 4, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 h\u1ecd t\u1eebng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf m\u00f9a b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/BXH-sau-vong-15-V-League.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HAGL th\u0103ng ti\u1ebfn tr\u00ean BXH V-League 2018</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC v\u1eabn gi\u1eadm ch\u00e2n \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 12 v\u1edbi 13 \u0111i\u1ec3m. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c TP.HMC g\u1eb7p Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ng\u00e0y mai, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a nh\u00f3m cu\u1ed1i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb thay \u0111\u1ed5i. Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh l\u00fac n\u00e0y ch\u1ec9 k\u00e9m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i TP.HCM, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em. Khi \u0111\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd c\u00f2n tr\u1edf n\u00ean n\u00f3ng b\u1ecfng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa gi\u1eefa 4 CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n, TP.HCM, Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh v\u00e0 SLNA.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-sai-gon-vong-15-vleague-2018-372-189256.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/ket-qua-hagl-vs-sai-gon-tran-dau-vong-15-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-sai-gon-vong-15-vleague-2018-372-189256.html\">HAGL 3-2 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n (KT): \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng</span><br>\r\nB\u1ecb S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC d\u1eabn b\u00e0n t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm nh\u01b0ng HAGL \u0111\u00e3 ng\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f2ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-2 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i ba tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n thua. Ba b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 gi\u00e0nh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3772","checkdouble":"189290"},{"date":"21:39 22/06","title":"Thanh H\u00f3a th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/30/thanh-hoa-thang-tran-thu-3-hlv-nguyen-duc-thang-het-loi-khen-ngoi-hoc-tro.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 3-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Becamex B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thanh H\u00f3a th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thanh H\u00f3a th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/HLV-Duc-Thang-ly-giai-viec-tin-tuong-thu-mon-Bui-Tien-Dung-hinh-anh.JPG\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi\u1ec1u t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/6, CLB FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0. H\u1eebng h\u1ef1c kh\u00ed th\u1ebf sau hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00e0 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng s\u1edbm c\u00f3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng 10 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. D\u00f9 Ti\u1ebfn Linh c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng r\u00fat ng\u1eafn t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 62 nh\u01b0ng Ofere c\u0169ng nhanh ch\u00f3ng t\u00e1i l\u1eadp kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch hai b\u00e0n cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng sau \u0111\u00f3 1 ph\u00fat.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y, Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ed1p 5 tr\u00ean BXH v\u1edbi 22 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch gi\u1eefa h\u1ecd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u00fat ng\u1eafn xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. \u0110\u00e2y r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u1ea3 quan v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Thanh \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 gi\u00e0nh 3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp, HLV Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng: \u201cQua m\u1ed7i v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean s\u00e2n. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 FLC Thanh H\u00f3a \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tinh th\u1ea7n chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u1edf nh\u1eefng v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 1 th\u00e1ng r\u01b0\u1ee1i l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi nhau c\u1eadt l\u1ef1c, t\u1eeb c\u00e1c th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean s\u00e2n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e3 hi\u1ec3u hi\u1ec3u nhau nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 th\u00edch nghi v\u00e0 tu\u00e2n th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra, l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft d\u00ednh \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tuy\u1ebfn. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng r\u1eb1ng th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 gi\u1eef \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u1eadp chung cao \u0111\u1ed9 cho giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i t\u00f2a \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u01a1i d\u1eady tinh th\u1ea7n, kh\u00e1t khao thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 tinh th\u1ea7n \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, FLC Thanh H\u00f3a ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 g\u1eb7p H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c Th\u1eafng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Video: Thanh H\u00f3a 3-1 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (V\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018)<span class=\"Apple-tab-span\" style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span></strong></p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/22/Thanh-Hoa-3-1-Binh-Duong.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\" /></div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3771","checkdouble":"189291"},{"date":"22:04 22/06","title":"B\u1ecb c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n, HLV Qu\u1ea3ng Nam h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/4/bi-cam-quan-hlv-quang-nam-het-loi-khen-ngoi-tai-nang-cua-dang-van-lam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3 chi\u1ec1u 22/6, CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u2018c\u01b0a \u0111i\u1ec3m\u2019 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng FC c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. V\u00e0 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Tam K\u1ef3 chi\u1ec1u 22/6, CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u2018c\u01b0a \u0111i\u1ec3m\u2019 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng FC c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m. V\u00e0 ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn, HLV Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 15 V-League, CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Nam c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1ch H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 Tam K\u1ef3. V\u1edbi l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 V-League \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng d\u1ed3n l\u00ean t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean khi m\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f2n ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Stevens \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 35.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Qu\u1ea3ng Nam h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Qu\u1ea3ng Nam h\u1ebft l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/4/thu-mon-dang-van-lam-nhan-mua-loi-khen-sau-tran-gap-sai-gon-fc.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen c\u1ee7a HLV Qu\u1ea3ng Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi hi\u1ec7p 1 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Huy H\u00f9ng. Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, th\u1ebf ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Qu\u1ea3ng, tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi\u1ebfu may m\u1eafn, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chia \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng FC.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, HLV Ho\u00e0ng V\u0103n Ph\u00fac \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Qu\u1ea3ng Nam c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m sau h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1 c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng Ph\u00fac t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a n\u00e0y. Nh\u01b0ng trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n v\u1ec1 l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. T\u00f4i \u0111ang mong s\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o H\u00e0 Minh Tu\u1ea5n \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>T\u00f4i c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n d\u00e0nh l\u1eddi khen cho \u0110\u1eb7ng V\u0103n L\u00e2m khi anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t hay, c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ea3ng Nam\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, \u00a0tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd Nguy\u1ec5n \u0110\u1ee9c C\u1ea3nh t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u00e1ch l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 kh\u00f4ng t\u1ec7 v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a n\u00e0y gi\u00fap H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 4 v\u1edbi 23 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Qu\u1ea3ng Nam v\u1edbi 21 \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ee9ng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"BXH V-League 2018\" title=\"BXH V-League 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/BXH-sau-vong-15-V-League.png\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>BXH V-League 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br />\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size: 11.5pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: robotoslab-regular, serif; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3770","checkdouble":"189294"},{"date":"19:31 22/06","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 22/6: MU v\u00e0 Barca s\u1eafp trao \u0111\u1ed5i \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/3/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-226-MU-va-Barca-sap-trao-doi-bom-tan-hinh-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/6.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU v\u00e0 Barca s\u1eafp trao \u0111\u1ed5i &ldquo;bom t\u1ea5n&rdquo;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 226 MU v\u00e0 Barca s\u1eafp trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 226 MU v\u00e0 Barca s\u1eafp trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/3/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-226-MU-va-Barca-sap-trao-doi-bom-tan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Barca quan t\u00e2m Paul Pogba</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nTheo Don Balon, Barca v\u00e0 MU ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 trao \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, theo \u0111\u00f3 Paul Pogba s\u1ebd c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Camp Nou c\u00f2n Jordi Alba t\u1edbi Old&nbsp;Trafford theo chi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Simeone: &quot;\u1ede c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ronaldo xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc h\u01a1n Messi&quot;</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Diego Simeone ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u1edf c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u0110TQG CR7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n M10.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-dua-ve-4-ngoi-sao-o-he-2018-172-189281.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/31/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-dua-ve-4-ngoi-sao-o-he-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-dua-ve-4-ngoi-sao-o-he-2018-172-189281.html\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 4 ng\u00f4i sao \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</span><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 4 ng\u00f4i sao \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Daily Mail, HLV Maurizio Sarri s\u1eafp ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea \u00f4ng n\u00e0y mu\u1ed1n The Blues mua 4 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Napoli bao g\u1ed3m Jose Callejon, Dries&nbsp;Mertens, Elseid Hysaj v\u00e0 Raul Albiol.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Man City \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Mahrez v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u euro</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mahrez cua Leicester\" title=\"Mahrez cua Leicester\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/man-city-va-tottenham-nhan-tin-cuc-mung-vu-sao-khung-leicester.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Man City s\u1eafp c\u00f3 Mahrez&nbsp;</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Le Buteur, Man City \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Riyad Mahrez c\u1ee7a Leicester v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 75 tri\u1ec7u euro. Th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Hazard c\u00f2n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Chelsea th\u00ec \u0111\u1eebng m\u01a1 Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Thomas Meunier l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng khuy\u00ean nh\u1ee7 ng\u00f4i sao Eden Hazard n\u00ean chia tay Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 gia nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t CLB danh gi\u00e1 h\u01a1n nh\u01b0 Real Madrid hay Barcelona.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Bayern v\u00e0 Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Modric</h2>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/bayern-munich-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-sao-real-madrid-180-189278.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/11/bayern-munich-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-sao-real-madrid.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/bayern-munich-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-sao-real-madrid-180-189278.html\">Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Real Madrid</span><br>\r\nBayern Munich v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Luka Modric r\u1eddi Real Madrid, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Don Balon, Bayern v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real nh\u1eafm Thigago thay Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marca kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Real Madrid nh\u1eafm ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich thay th\u1ebf Mateo Kovacic. Los Blancos ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4 sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Juve n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Golovin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 226 MU v\u00e0 Barca s\u1eafp trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 226 MU v\u00e0 Barca s\u1eafp trao \u0111\u1ed5i bom t\u1ea5n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-226-MU-va-Barca-sap-trao-doi-bom-tan-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Juventus n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua Alex Golovin</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuttosport kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Juventus \u0111\u00e3 n\u00e2ng gi\u00e1 h\u1ecfi mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Aleksandr Golovin c\u1ee7a CSKA Moscow v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 25 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ebfn 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Jack Grealish</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">The Birmingham Mail \u0111\u01b0a tin Liverpool c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jack Grealish c\u1ee7a Aston Villa, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Anfield d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh chi 15 \u0111\u1ebfn 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3769","checkdouble":"189285"},{"date":"18:49 22/06","title":"Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec sao Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/11/bayern-munich-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-sao-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Luka Modric r\u1eddi Real Madrid, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bayern v\u00e0 Tottenham mu\u1ed1n mua Modric</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Luka Modric duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Toni Kroos h\u1ee3p th\u00e0nh b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m hay nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Munich v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Luka Modric r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Munich v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Luka Modric r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/22/Munich-va-Tottenham-dang-muon-dua-Luka-Modric-roi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Bayern v\u00e0 Tottenham h\u1ecfi mua Luka Modric\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nPhong \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t cao c\u1ee7a Modric gi\u00fap Real Madrid gi\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn. V\u1edbi phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Don Ba Lon, Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Tottenham \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Luka Modric r\u1eddi Real Madrid, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro cho ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n Modric \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Modric n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i, Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thay th\u1ebf ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/man-utd-da-mua-pogba-voi-gia-beo-bot-172-182819.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real nh\u1eafm Pogba c\u1ee7a MU </span>nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Modric\" title=\"tien ve Modric\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/bayern-munich-va-tottenham-dai-chien-vi-sao-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u00e1n Modric \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 35 tri\u1ec7u euro m\u00e0 Bayern Munich v\u00e0 Tottenham chi ra l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Los Blancos nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi Bayern Munich, h\u1ecd \u0111ang hy v\u1ecdng HLV ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia Niko Kovac c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Modric chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110\u1ee9c thi \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u1edbi Spurs, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 33 nh\u01b0ng Modric v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao trong m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ebfn hai m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u1eefa, kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a anh r\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n v\u1edbi Bayern Munich ho\u1eb7c Tottenham, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Modric \u0111ang c\u00f9ng \u0110T Croatia thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1985 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t khi ghi b\u00e0n trong 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca r\u00f4 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3768","checkdouble":"189278"},{"date":"18:27 22/06","title":"MU nh\u1eafm sao Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/8/17/mu-nham-sao-barca-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU mu\u1ed1n mua Jordi Alba c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mourinho v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Young l\u00e0 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a M.U, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Tuy nhi\u00ean, n\u0103m nay c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 33, \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Jordi Alba v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU mu\u1ed1n mua Jordi Alba v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/20/MU-muon-mua-Jordi-Alba-voi-gia-40-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nLuke Shaw \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi M.U, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. Everton nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1995, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Goodison Park ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, MU mua Dalot c\u1ee7a Porto, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf c\u1ea3i hai c\u00e1nh. Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n cho r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o cho Luke Shaw.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, theo Mirror, Mourinho v\u1eabn mu\u1ed1n mua th\u00eam h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Dalot. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 th\u1eadm ch\u00ed mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>MU nh\u1eafm Alba n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">MU mu\u1ed1n mua Jordi Alba c\u1ee7a Barca \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Don Balon c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i. T\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Mourinho \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"hau ve Jordi Alba\" title=\"hau ve Jordi Alba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/30/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-sao-khung-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU chi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Jordi Alba\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Alba v\u00e0 Barca c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2020, song \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng. Kh\u00fac m\u1eafc \u1edf m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111ang khi\u1ebfn b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nBarca c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eafm \u0111\u1ebfn Marcos Alonso c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Alba gia h\u1ea1n. \u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Barca nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, M.U ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/tottenham-muon-gay-soc-voi-sao-khung-barca-172-189262.html\" target=\"_blank\">Tottenham c\u0169ng quan t\u00e2m Alba</span>, song r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng M.U \u0111ang chi\u1ebfm l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf l\u1edbn h\u01a1n, b\u1edfi Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n l\u1edbn h\u01a1n ngo\u00e0i ra h\u1ecd c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 l\u01b0\u01a1ng r\u1ea5t cao cho ng\u00f4i sao 29 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Alba s\u1ebd n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00e1nh tr\u00e1i c\u1ee7a M.U, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3767","checkdouble":"189276"},{"date":"19:14 22/06","title":"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 4 ng\u00f4i sao \u1edf H\u00e8 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/31/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-dua-ve-4-ngoi-sao-o-he-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 4 ng\u00f4i sao \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri s\u1eafp ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng tin <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/sao-napoli-xac-nhan-chuyen-hlv-maurizio-sarri-den-chelsea-172-187232.html\" target=\"_blank\">Maurizio Sarri ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea</span> \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i The Blues v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 4 ng\u00f4i sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 4 ng\u00f4i sao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-dua-ve-4-ngoi-sao-o-he-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Maurizio Sarri s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf Conte</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo Mirror v\u00e0 ESPN, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, \u00f4ng Sarri s\u1ebd d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u00f3 th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 3 n\u0103m, t\u1ea1i Stamford Bridge \u00f4ng h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111ang gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft chuy\u1ec7n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi HLV Conte, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 vi\u1ec7c ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, hi\u1ec7n c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf Anh v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ra m\u1eaft \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua 4 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo Daily Mail, Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 4 ng\u00f4i sao \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Stones vs Dries Mertens\" title=\"Stones vs Dries Mertens\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/2/da-tang-cua-man-city-tiet-lo-bi-quyet-thang-nhu-che-tre.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua Dries Mertens</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nDries Mertens v\u00e0 Jose Maria Callejon l\u00e0 b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o m\u00e0 Sarri mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Stamford Bridge, m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. The Blues s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1ecf ra kho\u1ea3ng 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i ra HLV Sarri c\u00f2n mu\u1ed1n Chelsea mua h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i Elseid Hysaj. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i. Hi\u1ec7n Victor Moses l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i, v\u1edbi kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Hysaj ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Raul Albiol c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Sarri nh\u1eafm n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng vi\u1ec7c Gary Cahill \u0111\u00e3 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n David Luiz mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli mua th\u00eam trung v\u1ec7 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 hi\u1ec3u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Napoli Chelsea s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi ra kho\u1ea3ng 100 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, The Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Sarri s\u1ebd c\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 mua s\u1eafm \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3766","