m nay 22/6.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/thanh-hoa-vs-binh-duong-vong-15-vleague-2018-372-189257.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP THANH H\u00d3A VS B\u00ccNH D\u01af\u01a0NG</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3764","checkdouble":"189257"},{"date":"17:52 22/06","title":"K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/22/ket-qua-hagl-vs-sai-gon-tran-dau-vong-15-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f2ng 15 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n v\u00f2ng 15 V-League 2018 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 22/6.</h2>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 HAGL vs S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: 2-1<br>\r\nNg\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n: Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng (3'); C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng (10'); Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng (41')<hr>\r\n<br>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i kh\u00e1 cay \u0111\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i, HAGL b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 v\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean tham v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nhanh ch\u00f3ng b\u1ecb d\u1ed9i g\u00e1o n\u01b0\u1edbc l\u1ea1nh khi chuy\u00ean gia t\u1ea1o si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m Nguy\u1ec5n Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m HAGL khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n V\u0103n Ti\u1ebfn ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ee9ng ch\u00f4n ch\u00e2n nh\u00ecn b\u00f3ng \u0111i v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Minh Vuong ghi ban tran Da Nang vs HAGL\" title=\"Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n tr\u1eadn \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng vs HAGL\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/Da-Nang-2-1-HAGL-Chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap HAGL t\u1ea1m d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n thua s\u1edbm khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn h\u01a1n. V\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 sau \u0111\u00f3 \u00edt ph\u00fat, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t, s\u1ed1 10 c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap HAGL d\u1ec5 \u0111\u00e1 h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi l\u00e0m ch\u1ee7 th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c uy hi\u1ebfp khung th\u00e0nh S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. Tuy nhi\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda &ldquo;G\u1ed7&rdquo; d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m k\u00e9m ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c, nh\u1eefng C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng, V\u0103n Thanh, Vi\u1ec7t H\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u01b0\u1edfng nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7p 1 s\u1ebd kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a th\u00ec \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 41, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc sau pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Minh V\u01b0\u01a1ng. \u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 chi\u1ec1u cao 1m65 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1eafc \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec3m h\u00f3c gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">2-1 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1. Hai \u0111\u1ed9i ra s\u00e2n t\u1ea1m ngh\u1ec9.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3763","checkdouble":"189270"},{"date":"15:09 22/06","title":"Real Madrid nh\u1eafm ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 Barca n\u00e2ng c\u1ea5p tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/11/23/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Mateo Kovacic ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Marca c\u1ee7a TBN \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real Madrid. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 4 \u1edf h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 sau Kroos, Modric v\u00e0 Casemiro.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/Real-Madrid-muon-mua-Thiago-Alcantara-cua-Bayern-Munich-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u0103m nay Modric \u0111\u00e3 33 tu\u1ed5i, Los Blancos \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernaber mu\u1ed1n mua ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 m\u1edbi thay v\u00ec trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Mateo Kovacic.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh khi\u1ebfn Kovacic c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n, anh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch ra \u0111i. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m t\u1eeb ph\u00eda AC Milan v\u00e0 Juventus.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh, MU v\u00e0 Arsenal c\u0169ng \u0111ang quan t\u00e2m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua c\u1ef1u sao Inter Milan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef Kovacic \u1edf l\u1ea1i song h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. N\u1ebfu ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i,&nbsp;Los&nbsp;Blancos s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng gi\u1eef b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu c\u00f2n l\u00ean ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n thay th\u1ebf ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Real nh\u1eafm Thiago thay Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Thiago Alcantara c\u1ee7a Bayern Munich trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Mateo Kovacic ra \u0111i, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Marca c\u1ee7a TBN \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thiago Alcantara dinh chan thuong nghiem trong\" title=\"Thiago Alcantara d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2017/11/23/real-madrid-nham-nguoi-cu-barca-nang-cap-tuyen-giua.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real Madrid nh\u1eafm Thiago Alcantara thay Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Thiago ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Bayern Munich. HLV Julen Lopetegui \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u00e0&nbsp;mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a anh v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLopetegui v\u00e0 Thiago c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 th\u00e2n thi\u1ebft, \u00f4ng hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i t\u1edbi Real Madrid. \u0110\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Bayern Munich nh\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 45 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3762","checkdouble":"189259"}]}